# Azure AI Document Intelligence Assistant

## Overview

Azure AI Document Intelligence Assistant is a cloud-based AI platform that enables users to upload PDF and Word documents and interact with them using natural language.

The platform uses Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) to retrieve relevant information from uploaded documents before generating accurate, context-aware responses using Azure OpenAI.

---

## Features

- Upload PDF and Word documents
- Extract text using Azure AI Document Intelligence
- Store documents securely in Azure Blob Storage
- Generate vector embeddings
- Semantic search using Azure AI Search
- Chat with documents using Azure OpenAI
- Secure user authentication
- Cloud-native Azure deployment

---

